            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Mercurio <lb n="2"/>Cenacus queritur <lb n="3"/>de Vitalino et Nata<lb break="no" n="4"/>lino filio ipsius <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>iument<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">o</supplied> quod ei rap<lb break="no" n="6"/>tum est e<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> rogat <lb n="7"/>deum Mercurium <lb n="8"/>ut nec ante sa<lb break="no" n="9"/>nitatem </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> habeant nissi <note>sic</note> <surplus>nissi</surplus> repraese<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>taverint mihi iu<lb break="no" n="3"/>mentum quod r<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>puerunt et deo <lb n="4"/>devotionem qua<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied> <lb n="5"/>ipse ab his ex<lb break="no" n="6"/>postulaverit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gebet für Gerechtigkeit. (B): Abweichende Textgestaltung.</p>
            </div>
